---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Privacy — appelsin" locale="en">
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12">
		<a href="/en" class="mb-8 inline-block text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200">← Home</a>
		<h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Privacy</h1>
		<div class="space-y-5 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300">
			<p>
				appelsin.io processes the data needed to create events, let guests upload photos, and send access or download links.
			</p>
			<p>
				For guests we may store a display name, email and the photos uploaded to the event. Email is used to send photos or links after the event and is not shared for any other purpose.
			</p>
			<p>
				Photos are deleted after the event’s retention period, unless the host deletes the event earlier. Payment and accounting records are retained as required by law.
			</p>
			<p>
				Contact us at <a class="underline hover:text-white" href="mailto:hello@appelsin.io">hello@appelsin.io</a> for data questions or deletion requests.
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
